    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Definitely!!! That&#8217;s how I first tried a very similar drink called The Italian Greyhound. The bartender smoked the chilled glass with rosemary (!) then built the drink that they make with vodka not gin (I&#8217;m not really a vodka drinker, btw), strained it into the glass and topped with club soda. After I took a delightful sip and complimented her creation, she admitted she likes it even more topped with Prosecco, so I said let&#8217;s do that. Wow it was amazing!</p>
    </div>

