    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>If no one&#39;s mentioned it yet, which I highly doubt, Gentian is a plant with bright blue flowers that grows in colder regions.  Some species, I know, grow in the Adirondack mountains of New York state.  There&#39;s bottle gentian and fringed gentian and pale gentian.  They&#39;re beautiful.  Gentian extract is also an ingredient in Moxie soda.</p>
    </div>

