      <p>Hi there&#8230;I have never heard about Aperol, but your post made me remember my own tiny episode.</p>
<p>When I was young one day I had an occation to be with my boss lady after work. At the bar she ordered white wine and asked the bartender to drop a bit of &#8220;Picon&#8221; in it. It was a bitter liquor made from orange, and it added some richness to the wine, also gave me an impression of elegant growing-ups world&#8230; I tasted this Piconed white wine, and I liked it very much.</p>
<p>Now, I will try to find Aperol in Tokyo, here. Thank you.</p>
